        {
            "title": "中國國內液化天然氣價格創五年新低 因需求疲軟",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><span class=\"news-dateline\">【彭博】--</span> 中國國內<a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link\" data-ylk=\"slk:液化天然氣;sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link;itc:0\" href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/tag/液化天然氣\">液化天然氣</a>價格創下五年新低，主要因為供應充裕而冬季取暖需求低於預期。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">根據卓創資訊的數據，中國主要液化天然氣接收站最低價本周跌破每噸3500元人民幣，創下2021年年中以來的最低水平。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">以往液化天然氣價格通常會因冬季取暖需求增加而上漲，但今年由於氣溫整體偏暖並且經濟復甦乏力，液化天然氣市場持續降價。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">推薦閱讀：中國11月液化天然氣進口同比成長 前景依然黯淡</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">與此同時，隨著海運液化天然氣密集到港，庫存壓力上升。海關數據顯示，管道天然氣進口量也在增加。卓創資訊統計顯示，截至12月19日，液化天然氣接收站庫容率約73%，故不得不增加出貨量以緩解庫存壓力。卓創資訊的分析師預計價格可能在月底之前保持低位。</p><div class=\"bg-card-bg-1 -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-7340f781-8816-326c-af40-5956419d6b9d-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">原文標題China’s Domestic LNG Price Falls to Five-Year Low on Weak Demand</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">More stories like this are available on <a class=\"link\" data-ylk=\"slk:bloomberg.com;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">bloomberg.com</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">©2025 Bloomberg L.P.</p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E5%9C%8B%E5%85%A7%E6%B6%B2%E5%8C%96%E5%A4%A9%E7%84%B6%E6%B0%A3%E5%83%B9%E6%A0%BC%E5%89%B5%E4%BA%94%E5%B9%B4%E6%96%B0%E4%BD%8E-%E5%9B%A0%E9%9C%80%E6%B1%82%E7%96%B2%E8%BB%9F-033506201.html",
            "pub_date": "2025-12-23 12:05:53",
            "source": "yahoo_finance_asia",
            "kind": 1,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "彭博新聞午間分享 你會想知道的五件事",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">暫避違約</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">萬科延長境內債寬限期的議案獲債券持有人投票通過，暫時得以避免違約風險。儘管如此，該開發商的困境令持有其13億美元境外債的跨國投資者面臨的風險加劇。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">大膽行動</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">日本財務大臣向投機者發出嚴厲警告，稱對於日圓與基本面不符的匯率波動，當局必要時「可以放手」採取大膽行動，並表示日方在外匯市場採取行動有「自主決定權」。日圓周二表現優於其他G-10貨幣。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">不要「硬碰硬」</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">美國總統川普警告委內瑞拉總統馬杜羅不要挑戰美國，並說要留下一艘被美國扣押超級油輪上的石油，但他拒絕透露自己是否謀求推翻這位委內瑞拉領導人。</p><div class=\"bg-card-bg-1 -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-8f33e30f-3de1-3d87-93a8-4e1316e581a7-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">禁止銷售</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">美國聯邦通信委員會(FCC)宣布，今後將禁止大多數外國製造的無人機及無人機系統的關鍵部件，而中國無人機製造商大疆創新列入「受限實體名單」的截止日期亦即將到來。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">銷量領先</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">華為超豪華轎車尊界S800當下在中國備受歡迎，比保時捷Panamera、梅賽德斯-賓士集團的S級以及所有其他售價不低於10萬美元的車型都要暢銷。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">More stories like this are available on <a class=\"link\" data-ylk=\"slk:bloomberg.com;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">bloomberg.com</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">©2025 Bloomberg L.P.</p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E5%BD%AD%E5%8D%9A%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E%E5%8D%88%E9%96%93%E5%88%86%E4%BA%AB-%E4%BD%A0%E6%9C%83%E6%83%B3%E7%9F%A5%E9%81%93%E7%9A%84%E4%BA%94%E4%BB%B6%E4%BA%8B-043111490.html",
